des:
Fish Tank Screensaver HD on your Echo Show or Echo Spot device (required a screen). Fish Tank plays a relaxing freshwater aquarium on your Echo Show or Echo Spot. Great fun for your living room, kitchen or bedroom! 

+ Ask "Alexa, open My Tank" to open skill. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
